# Redirect all traffic to https://etmcleaning.com (canonical URL)
# This ensures consistent URLs for SEO and prevents duplicate content penalties

# HTTP non-www to HTTPS non-www
http://etmcleaning.com/* https://etmcleaning.com/:splat 301!

# HTTP www to HTTPS non-www
http://www.etmcleaning.com/* https://etmcleaning.com/:splat 301!

# HTTPS www to HTTPS non-www
https://www.etmcleaning.com/* https://etmcleaning.com/:splat 301!
